{"tid":1974710,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【狗衝政府工?】公務員綜合招聘考試(CRE)及基本法測試6月舉行 現接受申請","createTime":"2020-04-16T04:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:20:26.000Z","uid":116083,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0500152329d21add5ce2a95a8f9b4f13818bec4d","tid":1974710,"uid":116083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"政府將於2020至2021年度招聘超過一萬名公務員，填補退休空缺和預算案中新增的約6000個職位，包括學位或專業程度公務員職位。新一輪的綜合招聘考試及基本法測試明日起接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n考試暫定6月6日及13日舉行，或如有需要，將於6月內的其他日期舉行。應徵學位或專業程度公務員職位的人士，必須具備有效的綜合招聘考試成績，除非應徵者持有中學文憑考試或其他訂明的公開考試的同等成績。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，公務員事務局會因應新型冠狀病毒疫情發展，在有需要的情況下對考試作出新安排，並在公務員事務局網頁公布，提醒有意參加考試人士留意最新公布。政府亦會在試場採取預防措施，保障考生和監考人員的健康，包括在試場入口設置體溫監察站，要求所有人在試場內戴上口罩及擴闊考生座位之間距離等。如有需要，考試會分多日舉行，以減少每日在試場的考生人數及確保考生之間的社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520736-20200415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520736-20200415.htm&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=135090e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520736-20200415.htm&h=a9f5fcb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520736-20200415.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n申請：<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/recruit/cre/949.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Frecruit%2Fcre%2F949.html&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d3060717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/recruit/cre/949.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人工參考：<br />\n<br />\nExecutive Officer II 二級行政主任<br />\n(MPS 15 &ndash; 27)<br />\n$31,750 &ndash; $55,995<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/executive-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fexecutive-officer%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=74cdf907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/executive-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nAssistant Trade Officer II 二級助理貿易主任<br />\nManagement Services Officer II 二級管理參議主任<br />\n(MPS 14 &ndash; 27)<br />\n$30,235 &ndash; $55,995<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/trade-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Ftrade-officer%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=de3424bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/trade-officer/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/management-services-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fmanagement-services-officer%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=4a5df9a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/management-services-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nAssistant Clerical Officer 助理文書主任<br />\n(MPS 3 &ndash; 15)<br />\n$15,555 &ndash; $31,750<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/clerical-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fclerical-officer%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=21f753be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/clerical-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nPolice Constable 警員<br />\n(PPS 3 &ndash; 15)<br />\n$25,380 &ndash; $40,610*<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fpolice-constable%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=c04b0479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/</a>"},{"pid":"22a11de53242ebcf5cf21349d6d25d828f71e057","tid":1974710,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"獨派手足滲透時間！"},{"pid":"1901cfe6bec1d0648f923e3832277a868eaeeff3","tid":1974710,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"考CRE 用EO 做參考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38cb9c0f620940b48b7c159aa7f2202fdb69469","tid":1974710,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a11de53242ebcf5cf21349d6d25d828f71e057","tid":1974710,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"獨派手足滲透時間！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}